Description_lang: N'Zoth taps into players' minds and evokes their darkest thoughts, inflicting $s1 Shadow damage every $t1 sec for $d.Upon expiration, Evoke Anguish leaves behind a pool of Anguish, which grows briefly after spawning.Every time N'Zoth the Corruptor casts Evoke Anguish, all other pools of Anguish grow in size.
